cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MA, cs.RO, cs.SY. 

The paper deals with cooperative multiagent reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) that involves multiple agents interacting with each other and their environment. The paper also involves the use of deep function approximation (cs.AI) and temporal abstraction (cs.RO) to address the challenges of long horizons and continuous states/actions. The paper is specifically focused on teaching policies (cs.MA) and their effectiveness in improving team-wide learning progress. Finally, the paper deals with systems (cs.SY) involving multiple agents and their interactions.
